
Put the following files in a folder:
optiboot_atmega328pb.hex
avrdude.conf


In a therminal, navigate to the folder and execute
>>>> remember to change the programmer name (-c flag) <<<<

avrdude -C ./avrdude.conf -p m328pb -c avrispmkII -B 4.25 -e -U lfuse:w:0xbf:m -U hfuse:w:0xde:m -U efuse:w:0xf4:m

avrdude -C ./avrdude.conf -p m328pb -c avrispmkII -B 4.25 -e -U flash:w:./optiboot_atmega328pb.hex
